467
00:29:09,240 --> 00:29:10,250
A wall.

468
00:29:11,750 --> 00:29:13,140
A whole wall of wine?

469
00:29:13,750 --> 00:29:15,490
A wall of wine, you two…

470
00:29:16,750 --> 00:29:19,570
