555
00:35:12,920 --> 00:35:13,460
I...

556
00:35:13,480 --> 00:35:14,210
Go back quickly.

557
00:35:15,480 --> 00:35:16,260
Go back.

558
00:35:20,070 --> 00:35:21,460
